snippet.title: Warhammer 40.000 Gladius - Chaos Space Marines || Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Gladius' Chaos Space Marines DLC is OUT NOW!
🎮 Get it on Steam 👉 http://bit.ly/2LXEeMT
💬 Join the Discord Server 👉 https://discord.gg/CyBavXBcad
🦎 Get it on Slitherine Store 👉 https://bit.ly/3eGuFOU

Warhammer 40,000: Gladius is back with a new playable faction, the Chaos Space Marines. Fueled by their hatred for the Imperium, these ancient warriors are ready to conquer Gladius Prime, killing and enslaving all who oppose them. In the name of the Warmaster, and their Dark Gods.
